OL,3,CFire crews tackle blaze at city
OL,4,CCathedral
OL,6,FFirefighters have tackled a fire on
OL,7,Fthe top of Liverpool's Anglican
OL,8,FCathedral.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called at
OL,11,F14.44 on Friday 1 May to to reports of
OL,12,Fa fire at the top of the tower, with
OL,13,Fsmoke visible.
OL,15,FCrews from Merseyside Fire and Rescue
OL,16,Farrived at the scene five minutes
OL,17,Flater and confirmed this was an
OL,18,Felectrical fire on the balcony on the
OL,19,Ftop floor of the cathedral.
OL,20,FFirefighters fought the fire, and the
OL,21,Fbuilding was evacuated.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
